{"tid":2047894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CuMask BFE僅82.6%遠遜官方聲稱標準 創科局：不評論坊間測試，總之用得啦","createTime":"2020-06-02T12:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T12:43:18.000Z","uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2097b5dc2d356ec53d6232d86cfba01a2c6c99dd","tid":2047894,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:06:08.000Z","msg":"港府早前動用8億公帑，向全港市民派發「銅芯抗疫口罩（CuMask）」，惟該口罩被專家連環踢爆抗菌能力差劣。本地口罩工廠「mask lab」以濾芯測試機，測試CuMask的「細菌過濾率（BFE）」，結果顯示其BFE僅有約83%，遠比國際最低級別低，更發現其有濾芯過濾率不一的缺點。創科局回覆指，不評論坊間其他測試，並重申CuMask已經由國際認可驗證，PFE、BFE等過濾效率均符合美國ASTM一級標準（95%）。<br />\n<br />\nmask lab今日（1日）動用廠內一部自動濾芯測試機，分別測試CuMask及另外兩款市面有售外科口罩的過濾率。結果顯示，兩款市面口罩過濾效果出眾，BFE均達98%或以上，而CuMask則僅有82.6%，遠低於美國ASTM最低95%的標準。<br />\n<br />\n測試更發現，相比較粗空氣微粒，CuMask在阻隔較細的微粒時效果反而更好，廠方認為該現象反映口罩的濾芯不平均，令口罩不同位置的過濾效果不一。<br />\nBFE測試結果遠低於政府聲稱95%<br />\n<br />\nmask lab今次用作測試口罩的儀器為中國製造，但聲稱與業界公認最好、美國製的「TSI8130」做過校正，結果十分準確。工廠負責人Albert重申，廠方儀器主要以「相對數據」確保生產上的品質管制，故今次測試結果僅為參考數據。翻查CuMask政府官網，聲稱口罩BFE達至美國ASTM的一級標準（95%），與今次測試結果不符。<br />\n<br />\n創科局回覆《蘋果》查詢時指，不會評論坊間其他測試，並重申CuMask已經由國際認可驗證，PFE、BFE等過濾效率，以及口罩阻燃性及壓力差方面，均符合美國ASTM一級標準（95%）。"},{"pid":"43c8fcaadea4be228e92da290efa61f6999086df","tid":2047894,"uid":37874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:08:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebce06979e49c0c65287b8268c2b4dfb8e25044","tid":2047894,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"呢個政府有無一樣野係做得好同做得掂"},{"pid":"5718a0986d2d5e57e7bde5c841557cc9ffa6f249","tid":2047894,"uid":39777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"差不多先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果然同支那接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf5e4a0b6d16dfc67c44a225b23f849e2157f5c","tid":2047894,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"港共: 你地使用不當<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c541c569d9fff142ba8c0c668aeec4e11e33a0","tid":2047894,"uid":45936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"最好多d on9用，攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e775c3fdcdd2ff4dd330733eafefd0758616dc","tid":2047894,"uid":19353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"官方： 錢已袋 評你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4201332ff82b4b304b544efce8500f0dfea7aec3","tid":2047894,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4539417/org/58bb76c71e4a1af9cb8811daf373b740.jpg/G3jjoLIvOU5YGut3cHJZPKtj2O7KtxTz7cY-X-3GPl8?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4539417%2Forg%2F58bb76c71e4a1af9cb8811daf373b740.jpg%2FG3jjoLIvOU5YGut3cHJZPKtj2O7KtxTz7cY-X-3GPl8%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=a8e5dc14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁海關去拉得人未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d834483f3c5494b740af169d9b9f5e9167b6ec","tid":2047894,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:41:42.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得會有本地爆發"},{"pid":"e16bd3ec961e97cc3d41893764d2a18c867dd6aa","tid":2047894,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"諗唔明 點解隔細粒子會勁過隔粗粒子"}]}